1.title: Woman for Single Dad
1.plot: Single dads Mike and Jake invite women they've only met online to move in with them and their respective children. Sparks fiy immediately for Mike and Valene while Jake and Ami suffer through an awkward first encounter.

2.title: Hubba Hubba
2.plot: When a sitter falls through Mike brings Mikey on his first date with Valene. Jake and Ami struggle to connect causing Jake to do something drastic. And single-dad Jason invites Sarah to live with him and his 2 daughters.

3.title: Disappearing Dad
3.plot: A furious Ami wonders if Jake's coming back after he stays out all night. Mike and Valene prep for Mikey's birthday party but someone's being a party pooper. Denise shares a personal secret with John. Paul tells Kallie how many kids he has.

4.title: The Ex Files
4.plot: Valene meets Mikey's Mom at his birthday party and tensions flare. Kallie considers backing out of going to Mississippi to meet Paul and his kids. Denise finally meets John and Elijah and one of them has a meltdown.

5.title: Adventures in Babysitting
5.plot: Jake and Ami share a romantic evening. Denise babysits rambunctious Elijah. Kallie confronts Paul over whether he's brought her to Mississippi for the right reasons. Valene grows frustrated when it becomes clear she's not the top priority in Mike's life.

6.title: Mixed Messages
6.plot: Mike and Valene go from hot to ice cold. John and Denise share an intimate moment. Jason's daughter Sidney doesn't want a replacement Mom. Things heat up for Paul and Kallie when they talk about sex. Jake confesses his true feelings for Ami - to his sister.

7.title: Still Single?
7.plot: John and Denise share a not so romantic Thanksgiving together. Sarah finally meets Jason's elusive ex. Mike and Valene have their first big fight. Paul and the kids head to NC with Kallie to meet her family. Jake questions his relationship with Ami.

imdb.plot outline: Single Dad Seeking follows five single fathers working hard to raise their kids. As they strive to provide the ideal lives for their sons and daughters, they each feel that a critical piece of their family is missing. These dedicated dads are searching to find not only love in their lives, but also a woman willing to love their children. Enter five women, each without children of her own, seeking her happily ever after with a responsible, caring man. In addition to finding love, these women sincerely want to be mothers. None of them have found the opportunity--until now.
